---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Tomfoolery" description="A little about Tom.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl reveal is-visible">
    <span class="badge">about</span>
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mt-2">
      What I do, roughly
    </h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <em>Placeholder — tell me what you want here and I'll rewrite it.</em>
        For now: I'm into electric vehicles (currently driving an IONIQ 5),
        specialty coffee, Pokémon TCG and blind-box figures, and dragging
        friends and family out on outdoor retreats I plan myself. Sci-fi
        fan — Star Wars, Star Trek — and I like experimenting with
        psychedelic-leaning AI art.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is where all of that lives in one place, instead of
        scattered across apps.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 tile inline-block">
      <span class="badge">say hi</span>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm">
        <em>Add your preferred contact link/email here.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
